Xenoplague is an in-game secret tech.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PARASITIC_SPRAY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Parasitic Spray</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Chmura pasożytów</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">PARASITIC_SPRAY</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Shoot an infectious spray.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Wystrzeliwuje chmurę pasożytów.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">REGENERATION_CLOUD</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Regenerative Spore Cloud</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Chmura zarodników regenerujących</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="60"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">REGENERATION_CLOUD</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Hero gains a regenerative spore cloud, healing itself and adjacent friendly Biological and Cyborg units for {RegCloudHeal}[hp/] at the end of each turn in tactical combat.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bohater otrzymuje chmurę zarodników regenerujących, dzięki czemu on i wszystkie przyjazne sąsiadujące jednostki organiczne i cyborgi na koniec każdej tury w walce taktycznej odzyskują {RegCloudHeal}[hp/].</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.
Biological and Cyborg are unit types</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">RAPID_MOVEMENTS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Rapid Movements</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Gwałtowne ruchy</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="60"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">RAPID_MOVEMENTS</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">The hero learns to move rapidly to confuse enemies. The hero gains [abilityblue]Skitter[/abilityblue], making them harder to hit if they move during their turn.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bohater porusza się gwałtownie, żeby zmylić przeciwników. Bohater zyskuje umiejętność [abilityblue]smyrg[/abilityblue], przez co trudniej go trafić podczas ruchu w jego turze.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.
Skitter is an in-game unit ability</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="30"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SPORE_FEEDING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">NAME</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Spore Feeding</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Pokarm dla zarodników</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill name.
'Feeding' as in the spores feed off of their targets</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="105"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SPORE_FEEDING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">The hero surrounds their army with spores that feed on their unit's kills to regenerate their Hit Points. Biological and Cyborg units in the hero's army regain {sporefeedinghealth} when they kill a Biological or Cyborg unit within {sproefeedingrange} hexes of them.[br/]Only functions when the hero is the army's commander.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Bohater otacza swoją armię zarodnikami, które żywią się trupami, by regenerować punkty wytrzymałości jednostek. Jednostki organiczne i cyborgi w armii bohatera odzyskują {sporefeedinghealth}, kiedy zabiją jednostkę organiczną lub cyborga w promieniu {sproefeedingrange} pól od nich.[br/]Możliwe tylko wtedy, gdy ten bohater jest dowódcą armii.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Skill description.
Biological and Cyborg are unit types
Commander in this case means an army leader, NOT the player character</Data></Cell></Row><Row ss:AutoFitHeight="0" ss:Height="45"><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">SPORE_FEEDING</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">UNIT_DESCRIPTION</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">This unit regains {sporefeedinghealth} when they kill a Biological or Cyborg unit within {sporefeedingrange} hexes.</Data></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Jednostka odzyskuje {sporefeedinghealth}, kiedy zabije jednostkę organiczną lub cyborga w promieniu {sproefeedingrange} pól.</Data></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Unit buff description.</Data></Cell></Row><Row><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell><Data ss:Type="String"/></Cell><Cell ss:Index="7"><Data ss:Type="String">Text between {} should NOT be localized as they are numerical values in-game. Text between [] should NOT be localized as they are either icons or text formatting

EXAMPLE: "Hero gains {PersonaAccDmg} increased damage and accuracy " looks in-game like "Hero gains +5 increased damage and accuracy"</Data></Cell></Row></Table><WorksheetOptions xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:excel"><Unsynced/><Selected/><Panes><Pane><Number>3</Number><ActiveRow>12</ActiveRow><ActiveCol>8</ActiveCol></Pane></Panes><ProtectObjects>False</ProtectObjects><ProtectScenarios>False</ProtectScenarios></WorksheetOptions></Worksheet></Workbook>